title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Nov 9 2021

description:
Are vaccine mandates coming for your kids? The "Everything is racist" Democrat platform now extends to roads. Bill O'Reilly weighs in on the topics of the day and why he and Trump are hitting the road on a History Tour. Kyle Rittenhouse trial and the case for self-defense. Adam Schiff gets filleted by Morgan Ortagus, co-host of The View, on his Russian collusion lies.
